{"tid":1537001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正在宣布 十月一日 香港建國日！","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:34:44.000Z","uid":188691,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"666ff80f0cecc5e9629406626bb364d8e793d84c","tid":1537001,"uid":188691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:49:45.000Z","msg":"你慶生 我都慶生<br />\n清算都浪費心機<br />\n<br />\n唔好再對一國兩制打飛機<br />\n721之後已經冇左架喇<br />\n與其無止境輪迴<br />\n只要我地改變規則 就係成個遊戲嘅王者<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始有心理準備 調整策略<br />\n<br />\n十月一日 中共七十大壽<br />\n我地會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正式宣布 香港新政府成立</span></span><br />\n<br />\n直接宣布建國<br />\n<br />\n攬炒就係要你出兵 有種就強搶<br />\n<br />\n來吧 讓我地成為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新香港人！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ab2bf541629a2b78db164a40f2384b62e04a823b","tid":1537001,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:49:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b79116eef41677094af926d2cb1ec8ff18a80f89","tid":1537001,"uid":279090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ncZpCrp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FncZpCrp.png&h=f3baf601&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65d141beb06c864276ea63681defc0b1fd27dd6a","tid":1537001,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:54:04.000Z","msg":"十月革命勢不可擋"},{"pid":"4592d7f2628b98bb3928cd98ace8b4174665af67","tid":1537001,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:34:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}